Hey Y'all... Guess who's back? :P  I went through a really tough patch this past week  and went through alot of soul searching where even the smallest things got me upset.   I had a lot of self-doubt  and unsure what's the point of going on anymore.   My closest friend killed herself about a month back  and it took a really big toll on me  especially me as a human being  and all of my flaws. This just perpetuated over night as I lie in bed  thinking that everything can move on.  After talking with really good people and friends  I learned that maybe I cant ignore my past  but I can not let it get the better of me  because apparantly  some of y'all really liked my memes :P.   And while they rarely get many likes  or nearly as many likes as the other picture memes  as a friend put it "you're probably going to be slept on by people who don't appreciate effort/clever jokes as much as some people; but for what it's worth  those people would double-like your posts if they could."  Anyways  Sorry for this long rant-ish post.   Once you get to know me  you know I have severe ups and downs  but usually I can quell them.   I Think I can find genuine happiness in knowing I can make another person smile. So I'm back  and I'm here to stay as your resident OC straight off the grill memer.   Thank you to Joshua Richardson Joseph Bae Andrew Wong Alex Flores Escarcega Dylan Kan Jordan Cope Manuel Aguilar Delong Lin James Markert Julia Martinez Anna Qi Vaishnavi Patel Hyunjin Thomas Park.
